fields.title: Senior PHP-программист (HighLoad)
Python Developer (Middle)
Senior Ruby Developer
fields.description:
Eastern Peak is looking for an experienced Ruby engineer to join the team. Join us and use your experience to promote the quality of the world’s most advanced visual test automation service, trusted and used by hundreds of the world’s leading software development teams.

Our customer is a world-known product that offers a unique, fully automated UI validation framework. Developed in-house, this Artificial Intelligence powered service utilizes new technologies in image processing.

Requirements:

    At least 3 years of work experience with Ruby
    Work experience with RSpec

An advantage:

    Work experience with Ruby C extensions
    Know how to work with Ruby multithreading
    Understanding of the basics of Android / iOS application development
    Experience in planning and setting up CI / CD solutions
    Familiarity with Java/C#

Responsibilities:

    Design, develop and ship new functionality on Ruby
    Performance analysis and optimization by removing roadblocks, increasing testability, and simplifying architecture to meet high standards.

We offer:

    Focused, friendly place, at the heart of new technologies, where you can grow your career
    Comfortable, modern and green office
    Flexible work schedules
    Work from home, when projects/clients allow
    Social package: paid sick leave and vacation
    Real Football, English courses, unlimited milk, fresh fruit and other goodies + medical insurance
    Green room with ping-pong and kicker.
